Package: studyplan
Title: Statistical Analysis Plan
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mingrui", "Xu", , "rui9_666@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tool for clinical trial planning, allowing users to
    calculate required sample sizes, evaluate statistical power, and
    analyze study feasibility based on budget constraints. It includes
    functions for sample size calculations and for modeling the trade-offs
    between total enrollment and the size of expensive subgroups.
